narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Gambrills Sisters Health Care is a Clinic/Center, Mental Health (Including Community Mental Health Center) provider based in Gambrills, MD. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $511K in Medicaid payments across 6K claims serving 1K beneficiaries.
